A single woman walks down Pontocho, a usually bustling alley of restaurants and bars. Due to Coronavirus-related restrictions on hours and alcohol, it's quiet this evening; perfect for a photographer looking for a clear shot.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
一人の女性が先斗町を歩きます。 それは通常、レストランやバーのにぎやかな通りです。 しかし、新コロナウイルスに関連した時間とアルコールの制限のため、今夜は静かです。 シンプルな写真をお探しの写真家に最適です。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html">A single woman walks down Pontocho, a usually bustling alley of restaurants and bars. Due to Coronavirus-related restrictions on hours and alcohol, it's quiet this evening; perfect for a photographer looking for a clear shot.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2105_IMG_3377.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Seiryo-ji・清涼寺</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210511/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Seiryo-ji・清涼寺" /><published>2021-05-11T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-05-11T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/seiryoji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210511/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
