&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;The original school building (right) has been preserved as a community center. A grassy area (left) next to the Takase River is a nice gathering spot, with coffee shops adjacent.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
旧立誠小学校の所で、現祭公開のゲートホテル京都高瀬川。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
	右、旧校舎が公民館を使用されています。左、草な「立誠広場」です。

